Only females of the sexual generation have been described, which induce integral leaf galls on an undetermined 
<taxonomicName box="[285,379,1852,1878]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
